Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同千年的時光相比不過是一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可對我而言卻好像是永恆的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在祓禊之儀前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴空下 靈竺樹茂密的樹葉在強風中搖曳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訴說著你的不歸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 從那天開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.35,0:01:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你這雙直率的雙瞳卻一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬雲之女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉多年來未曾問候過您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖諾瓦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎能忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想再見您一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得會與你再度重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那一天開始 我就一直在等待著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大巡禮之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾多的靈魂會被吞沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那黑色的暗影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑暗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這胸中才會空空如也嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要帶走胎動窟裡的住民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真會開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人是為了糾正扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自願彙集到這日輪之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並獻出自己的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此將自己化為光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也無權吞噬他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就試著接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受我 接收這寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道我的名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是玩的很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕撫的微風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼老的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽映照下的舊水塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑪烏之原…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的黑影?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我最初與最後的怨敵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那次邂逅的一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填滿我空蕩蕩的胸膛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我 我是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賦予…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給明之了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我也感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨的時候 聽到了你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以肯定能傳連到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便相隔遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們也會通過靈魂聯繫在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽出事那天 明之不就是這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有話要說給你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在我先不說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們一定會重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒有說出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會說給你聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在尖端島 等著我吧 春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在尖端島 等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後一次回頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 綠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太荒唐了 這算什麼引導
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亞美拜託我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我盡快帶大家離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亞美?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故鄉的泰斯克人都叫她 「天女大人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個背叛了聖諾瓦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從龍宮逃出去的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識她?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡那個「天女大人」吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我說中了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命原本就是由生死兩面構成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一面更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是由所有者本人決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為叛徒的天女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼資格說三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太荒謬了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只為死亡而活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留給他們的就只剩下終結了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今…已經無法阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我在遭到戰艦空襲的比丘禪鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了一個失去了母親的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而後便背離了聖諾瓦大人的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對您的教誨產生了懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也無法再相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷流浪的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某一天 被一艘郵政船收留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了諸多的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接觸到了人們的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也學會了因悲傷而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因歡樂而開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 在您所孕育的黑暗之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對一族的思念開始綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與亡念的扎穆德相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是違背您的教誨我也不得不告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去的話 就說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有資格接受祓禊之儀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻來到您面前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個虛假的天女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的敵人在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對其熟視無睹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懈怠之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懈怠之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懈怠之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一生都無法遇到你的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一生都不會真正的活著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我在尋找著…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人並不用尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們始終是在包圍著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我在等待…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去等待敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們時時刻刻都在侵犯我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時如果沒有你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也無法記起自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這次輪到我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你埋葬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 邂逅終將到來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的指甲 牙 耳朵 手足 都無法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雨水…是熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘缺的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有殘缺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面明明沒有主魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我也沒有靈魂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣就好的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就獻上這奈性命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我能高呼敵人時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我能高呼我的敵人時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會有一個邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被淋到的人趕快脫下衣物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把水擦掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個在這裡避雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去觀察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要攜起手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同構築泰斯克的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫吉蕾卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要回到聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰斯克人便能再度流淌高貴的血
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人一直對此深信不疑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您無論如何一定要回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說喪氣話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是泰斯克人民自立之時吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必來尋我的屍身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事我必須跟你說明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面開始吵鬧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去安靜的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是你與我初次見面的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 開始祓禊之儀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是自北方大地傳出第一聲嬰兒的啼哭開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖諾瓦一族代代相傳的秘笈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一族在這北國
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世代擔負著為皇帝的子嗣接生的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們那種只為吞噬其他靈魂而生的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為對此的補償
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的先祖收集希洛克…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育出扎穆德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們成為大巡禮的調和者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這一代的希洛肯皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我接生的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子生來就是一具屍骸 沒有哭聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配金剛塔的僧侶們…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為我們骯髒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們趕出了胎動窟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給那孩子的屍骸裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞入了人造希洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令他在淤塞中生存成長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我被趕出胎動窟後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的哭泣聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼嚎聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那天他接受了虛假的生命之後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直沒有停息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那歎息在我的心中孕育出了一個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不切斷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大巡禮這條悲哀的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我催生出無數的扎穆德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來與他相抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令那呼嚎聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸於虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子心中的悲傷很龐大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過龐大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要切斷傳承到我這代的聖諾瓦之血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我的身體與龍宮中帶來的太古希洛克融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注入到那孩子的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這樣您就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛散出來的希洛克…就會寄宿到現世的人們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法承受它的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都會變成石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同希洛克一起逝去的我會滌淨眾人的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是將他們帶回魯伊孔的洪流之中而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他們活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便那是骯髒的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然希望跟大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起生活在這片大地上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…無法獨自生活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能看著未來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的靈魂已經變得如此溫暖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖諾瓦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是微風輕撫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 祓禊之儀便完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬雲之女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我有了新名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫娜琪亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安歇吧 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖地被剝奪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在世界裡四處流浪 飽受欺凌…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在此一雪家族之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能只抓住仇恨不放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要斬斷的是泰斯克人民的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的仇恨就是我活著的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等待著誅殺你的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渺小的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太渺小了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連痛苦都稱不上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法成為宣洩的出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡的時刻終於來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻我究竟等了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖諾瓦大人再度駕臨胎動窟的這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那傢伙會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖諾瓦大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖諾瓦大人在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖諾瓦大人接受了我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將在下個千年來臨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大地充滿幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要關閉胎動窟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走 娜琪亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像分別了很久一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我駕划艇來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個有天分的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 幫我帶大家離開胎動窟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你 娜琪亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡楊格了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 我真希望能養育你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希羅扎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有被溫格羅封住的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能為大家打開它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一點沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便要我以性命交換
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我自己選擇的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是庫吉蕾卡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識一個人 她始終把你的照片帶在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人對我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨中是無法綻放出笑容的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都珍視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕陽沉入艷朝之森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群星從低語之泉升起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招魂之長呼喊著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人來迎接我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睜開水靈靈的眼睛笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個樣子讓我忍不住心生愛戀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會把你帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你戰鬥的時候總有一種親切的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我就是你內心中的另一個你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我內心中的…我?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我是你內心中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直喜愛著你 憎恨著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你一直努力到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把它給我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因為我不能把生命給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把唯一能識別我的東西 填入你空虛的胸膛裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把自己的名字給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:21:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會忘記自我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就現在 我把心房關上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還不能讓別人的聲音傳進來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次仰望夜空的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璀璨的星座或許改變了面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我想起它時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.33,0:22:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便會露出微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關閉的大門與睜開的雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又要再次回到那充滿歡笑與淚水的生活中了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.36,0:24:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.73,0:24:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨石與少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎 大家一直在等著你
